Thank you all for 1000 users! Everyone at ResourcePile is pleased to see how many people have come to use what we have created which began as a simple place to find your favourite maps from the Overcast Network. You can read more about this milestone here.
Overcast Map Collection
A collection of publicly downloadable maps from the Overcast Network.

 Warning

We are changing the way we handle public maps from the Overcast Network. Downloads for many maps may not work as expected, or at all, for the next few hours while we transition to this new system. We are also no longer supporting Cardinal servers with our repositories. This however doesn't mean you cannot include these collections on your Cardinal server, it just means you will get unsupported maps.
